name: WDJC
body: The WHET DJ Language Compiler for Musical Composition is a project by William Falk-Wallace, Hila Gutfreund, Emily Lemonier, and Thomas Elling for Columbia University's COMSW4115: Programming Languages and Translators Class in Fall 2013, taught by Stephen Edwards.
